## ✨ Features

- **Single-file** — entire portfolio in one `index.html`, zero dependencies to install
- **Dark theme** — custom CSS variables, noise overlay, gradient accents
- **Fully responsive** — mobile hamburger nav, fluid grids, clamp typography
- **Scroll animations** — `IntersectionObserver`-based reveal on scroll
- **Scroll progress bar** — fixed top indicator
- **Terminal card** — animated JetBrains Mono terminal widget (desktop only)
- **Resume download** — direct PDF served from `/resume.pdf`
- **Performance** — no frameworks, no build step, instant load

