## 🚀 Getting Started

### Run Locally

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Nadi1173/portfolio.git
cd portfolio

# Option 1 — Open directly in browser
open index.html

# Option 2 — Serve with Python (recommended for /resume.pdf to work)
python3 -m http.server 8080
# Visit http://localhost:8080


npm i -g vercel
vercel --prod

# Drag and drop the folder at https://app.netlify.com/drop
# OR use Netlify CLI
npm i -g netlify-cli
netlify deploy --prod --dir .


git init
git add .
git commit -m "feat: initial portfolio"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/Nadi1173/portfolio.git
git push -u origin main
# Enable GitHub Pages in repo Settings → Pages → main branch

